UPDATE channel SET
                version_id = $2,
                name = $3,
                description = $4,
                nsfw = $5,
                bitrate = $6,
                user_limit = $7,
                owner_id = $8,
                icon = $9,
                locked = $10,
                archived_at = $11,
                invitable = $12,
                type = $13,
                parent_id = $14
            WHERE id = $1
